1. Open file in editor
2. Enter "(", "[", "{" and make sure that ")", "]", "}"  is closed automatically
3. Open "Preferences->JavaScript->Editor->Typing"
4. Uncheck "(Parenthese), [square] brackets, {braces}" check-box and save change
5. Make sure that ")", "]", "}" is not closed automatically
